{"tid":374792,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［連鎖］越北-屌打-越棧","createTime":"2017-08-26T04:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T16:33:18.000Z","uid":43370,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2e6c153be63b043a24131fc7633b5d189ef1c6","tid":374792,"uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:47:21.000Z","msg":"就咁一碗生牛金邊粉比較<br />\n<br />\n牛肉：<br />\n越北-淋身易咬，上台時生既<br />\n越棧-好實好難咬，黎到已經熟左一半<br />\n<br />\n金邊粉：<br />\n越北-爽滑 量多<br />\n越棧-未咬就斷，好粉，量小<br />\n<br />\n湯：<br />\n越北-香濃夠味，但唔會好口喝<br />\n越棧-淡，飲唔出係乜野味<br />\n<br />\n越北下午茶既份量味道都完勝越棧正價時段，屌打成功"},{"pid":"9114e583ec28d91c2ad71b5bfa50fc16b50e1362","tid":374792,"uid":8216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:51:35.000Z","msg":"越一點睇？"},{"pid":"dd28565eb062a35617f1bc424afb9c0b95131330","tid":374792,"uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>越一點睇？</blockquote><br />\n未食過<br />\n搵日試下"},{"pid":"6ddb2ccd42d6b791fcfc94111fe3e5772c76f406","tid":374792,"uid":12271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"食開撈檬<br />\n未食過越北<br />\n好唔好食㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1fc393a341105f5db3cc2914472700815c2868","tid":374792,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"打手味濃"},{"pid":"8329cda326ed6792b803a56d089936a8cbefbd26","tid":374792,"uid":10038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"真心越北好味啲<br />\n不過芽莊最好"},{"pid":"0a257bc759102cdf18d921e9f8c3947997052250","tid":374792,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:38:44.000Z","msg":"越北係幾好食，同埋特飲真係幾特別。<br />\n但越南粉麵真係好少變化，食多幾次就厭。"},{"pid":"96ac851adce2ce1e7e8ee3761b4d98402a940f1a","tid":374792,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:20:59.000Z","msg":"價錢呢?"},{"pid":"a0320dcd9db84116534452eaa4085cc4f783df9b","tid":374792,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>價錢呢?</blockquote><br />\nlunch就4x，食開學生有折，好平，<br />\n夜晚好似5x，但冇野飲，好少夜晚食"}]}